data.description:
Beautiful two story home, private corner lot, adorable front porch, first floor has tile, living room with fireplace, dining room full of light, kitchen total remodeled 2021, has granite countertops, backsplash, stain stainless steel appliances, pantry, private dog room, water heater 2022, 2 car garage finished 425 SQ(heated- has his own unit HVAC),it has a side entrance ,can be used for game room or other, covered back patio with pavers entrance from the front, has a fire pit, perfect for entertaining, a large shed in the back corner.
Second floor has 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 full baths. New Flooring 2021 Vinal laminated water resistant, Master bedroom is spacious with lots of light, walk in closet, master bath has double sink, shower and bathtub. You must see, this house looks like a model home!. Community has a club house, beautiful pool, playgrounds, a pond and trails.
Enjoy it, one hour notice required for showing.
